Open configuration

GET 
/configurator/:version/configurator/open/:configurationId

This opens an existing configuration & continues the configuration session.

Request​

Path Parameters

    configurationId stringrequired

    Identifier of the configuration.

    version stringrequired

Query Parameters

    ignoreConflicts boolean

    If true, the API will (try) to resolve conflicts automatically

    includeSearchbarResults boolean

    Default value: true

    lang string

    The language to open the configuration in

Responses​

  • 200

Success

  • text/plain
  • application/json
  • text/json
  • Schema
  • Example (from schema)
